[[!meta title="New Staff Checklist"]]
# Things to do when you become...

## New Staff

* Be added to staff group on [Request Tracker](https://rt.ocf.berkeley.edu/)
* Be mentored on using [[OCF scripts|scripts]]
* Be added to group approve
* Optional: add yourself to the [[staff list|staff]]

## Privileged Staff

* [[Set up a wiki account|ikiwiki/editing-the-wiki]]
* Be mentored on using puppet
* Be granted a [[kerberos root principal|administrative_powers#rootprincipal]]

## Root Staff

* Be added to [[group admin|administrative_powers#admingroup]]

## Site Manager

* Be granted a [[kerberos admin principal|administrative_powers#adminprincipal]]
